{"data":[{"name":"82:1","price":"1. Cuando el cielo se resquebraje;","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنفَطَرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5830,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā al-samāu infaṭarat ","translations":["When","the sky","(is) cleft asunder","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","al-samāu","infaṭarat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,3289],[3,3289,4824]]}},{"name":"82:2","price":"2. cuando los astros se dispersen (abandonando sus órbitas);","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡكَوَاكِبُ ٱنتَثَرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5831,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-kawākibu intatharat ","translations":["And when","the stars","scatter","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-kawākibu","intatharat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,1980],[3,1980,4585]]}},{"name":"82:3","price":"3. cuando los mares se entremezclen;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ فُجِّرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5832,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-biḥāru fujjirat ","translations":["And when","the seas","are made to gush forth","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-biḥāru","fujjirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1680],[3,1680,2645]]}},{"name":"82:4","price":"4. cuando las tumbas expulsen a los muertos;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡقُبُورُ بُعۡثِرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5833,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-qubūru buʿ'thirat ","translations":["And when","the graves","are overturned","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-qubūru","buʿ'thirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1820],[3,1820,3305]]}},{"name":"82:5","price":"5. entonces, todos sabrán las buenas y las malas acciones que realizaron.","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّا قَدَّمَتۡ وَأَخَّرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5834,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalimat nafsun mā qaddamat wa-akharat ","translations":["Will know","a soul","what","it has sent forth","and left behind","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalimat","nafsun","mā","qaddamat","wa-akharat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,1520],[3,1520,2720],[4,2720,3820],[5,3820,5645]]}},{"name":"82:6","price":"6. ¡Oh, hombre (que niegas la verdad)!, ¿qué te sedujo y te apartó de tu Generoso Señor,","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ ٱلۡكَرِيمِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5835,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"yāayyuhā al-insānu mā gharraka birabbika al-karīmi ","translations":["O","man","What","has deceived you","concerning your Lord","the Most Noble","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yāayyuhā","al-insānu","mā","gharraka","birabbika","al-karīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2660],[2,2660,4540],[3,4540,4720],[4,4720,5850],[5,5850,6860],[6,6860,9425]]}},{"name":"82:7","price":"7. Aquel que te creó, te modeló con perfección y armonía","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّىٰكَ فَعَدَلَكَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5836,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī khalaqaka fasawwāka faʿadalaka ","translations":["Who","created you","then fashioned you","then balanced you","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","khalaqaka","fasawwāka","faʿadalaka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,1850],[3,1850,3170],[4,3170,4525]]}},{"name":"82:8","price":"8. y te concedió la apariencia que quiso?","arabic":"فِيٓ أَيِّ صُورَةٖ مَّا شَآءَ رَكَّبَكَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5837,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"fī ayyi ṣūratin mā shāa rakkabaka ","translations":["In","whatever","form","what","He willed","He assembled you","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","ayyi","ṣūratin","mā","shāa","rakkabaka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1580],[2,1580,2180],[3,2180,3130],[4,3130,4100],[5,4100,5580],[6,5580,7115]]}},{"name":"82:9","price":"9. Y, sin embargo, negáis el Día del Juico Final.","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5838,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā bal tukadhibūna bil-dīni ","translations":["Nay","But","you deny","the Judgment","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","bal","tukadhibūna","bil-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1240],[3,1240,2710],[4,2710,5555]]}},{"name":"82:10","price":"10. Y, en verdad, tenéis (ángeles) guardianes","arabic":"وَإِنَّ عَلَيۡكُمۡ لَحَٰفِظِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5839,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-inna ʿalaykum laḥāfiẓīna ","translations":["And indeed","over you","(are) surely guardians","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-inna","ʿalaykum","laḥāfiẓīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1320],[2,1320,2330],[3,2330,5395]]}},{"name":"82:11","price":"11. que son honorables, registran (todas vuestras acciones)","arabic":"كِرَامٗا كَٰتِبِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5840,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"kirāman kātibīna ","translations":["Noble","recording","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["kirāman","kātibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,4255]]}},{"name":"82:12","price":"12. y saben lo que hacéis.","arabic":"يَعۡلَمُونَ مَا تَفۡعَلُونَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5841,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"yaʿlamūna mā tafʿalūna ","translations":["They know","whatever","you do","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["yaʿlamūna","mā","tafʿalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1620],[3,1620,4205]]}},{"name":"82:13","price":"13. Ciertamente, los creyentes piadosos gozarán de las delicias (del paraíso);","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٖ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5842,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-abrāra lafī naʿīmin ","translations":["Indeed","the righteous","(will be) surely in","bliss","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-abrāra","lafī","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,2440],[3,2440,3090],[4,3090,5225]]}},{"name":"82:14","price":"14. mientras que los pecadores incrédulos estarán en el fuego (del infierno),","arabic":"وَإِنَّ ٱلۡفُجَّارَ لَفِي جَحِيمٖ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5843,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-inna al-fujāra lafī jaḥīmin ","translations":["And indeed","the wicked","(will be) surely in","Hellfire","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-inna","al-fujāra","lafī","jaḥīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2560],[3,2560,3150],[4,3150,5545]]}},{"name":"82:15","price":"15. en el que entrarán el Día del Juicio Final","arabic":"يَصۡلَوۡنَهَا يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5844,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"yaṣlawnahā yawma al-dīni ","translations":["They will burn (in) it","(on the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["yaṣlawnahā","yawma","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1490],[2,1490,2080],[3,2080,4515]]}},{"name":"82:16","price":"16. y del que no podrán salir (jamás).","arabic":"وَمَا هُمۡ عَنۡهَا بِغَآئِبِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5845,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā hum ʿanhā bighāibīna ","translati